          <p style={{fontWeight:300,color:"rgba(255,255,255,0.72)",fontSize:14,lineHeight:1.8,marginBottom:24}}>I offer flexible flat rate fee structures that can save you thousands. Reach out and I will personally walk you through what is available.</p>
